OL,3,CDouble-amputee Ghurka veteran receives
OL,4,CMBE
OL,6,FMr Budha Magar said: "I'm delighted
OL,7,Fand honoured to be recognised for work
OL,8,FI (am) doing.
OL,10,F"I'm here to send a positive message
OL,11,Faround the world. This is my aim...
OL,12,Fsomething of hope and optimism."
OL,14,FMr Budha Magar successfully campaigned
OL,15,Fto the Supreme Court in Nepal to
OL,16,Foverturn a ban on people with
OL,17,Fdisabilities climbing Everest in 2018,
OL,18,Fbefore making mountaineering history
OL,19,Fhimself in 2023.
