OL,7,Fdevelopments at the moment and I hope
OL,8,Fthat our future generations of DAK
OL,9,Fwill benefit," he said.
OL,11,FAfter becoming an MBE, Mr Budha Magar
OL,12,Ftravelled to Alaska where he plans to
OL,13,Fsummit Mount Denali.
