OL,3,CDouble-amputee Ghurka veteran receives
OL,4,CMBE
OL,6,FMr Budha Magar said: "This is the
OL,7,Ffirst time ever I think a double above-
OL,8,Fknee amputee is attempting that
OL,9,Fmountain and... to show that people
OL,10,Fwith disabilities, we can do
OL,11,Fsomething, we are capable to do, live,
OL,12,Flike other people, we can live a
OL,13,Fsuccessful and meaningful life and
OL,14,Fhappy life."
OL,16,FHe is also currently fundraising for a
OL,17,Ftarget of #884,900 ` the height of
OL,18,FEverest "plus two 00s" for five
OL,19,Fcharities close to his heart that
OL,20,Fsupported him since losing his legs.
