OL,3,CDouble-amputee Ghurka veteran receives
OL,4,CMBE
OL,6,FThe father-of-three joined the Royal
OL,7,FGurkha Rifles at the age of 19 and
OL,8,Fwhile serving in Afghanistan he
OL,9,Fstepped on an improvised explosive
OL,10,Fdevice (IED) and lost both legs in
OL,11,F2010.
OL,13,FHe said growing up in Nepal people
OL,14,Fwith disabilities were seen as a
OL,15,F"burden of the earth" and disability
OL,16,Fwas perceived as a sin from previous
OL,17,Flives.
OL,19,F"When I lost my legs, I thought my
OL,20,Flife is finished," he said.
