OL,3,CDouble-amputee Ghurka veteran receives
OL,4,CMBE
OL,6,F"I really wasted my time, about two
OL,7,Fyears of my time, just not knowing
OL,8,Fwhat to do and just getting depressed
OL,9,Fand trying to take my life.
OL,11,F"I think if I was aware of disability
OL,12,Fthen I didn't have to go through all
OL,13,Fof this. I wasn't very educated and
OL,14,Faware. So now my aim is to just climb
OL,15,Fthe mountain and (raise) awareness of
OL,16,Fdisability as much as I can."
