OL,3,CDouble-amputee Ghurka veteran receives
OL,4,CMBE
OL,6,FMr Budha Magar believes things have
OL,7,Fcome "some way" in progress in
OL,8,Fdisability awareness among people with
OL,9,Fdisabilities but also society at
OL,10,Flarge, but there still remains "a long
OL,11,Fway to go".
OL,13,F"Just me being myself, I can do so
OL,14,Fmuch, right?" he said.
OL,16,F"This is why I'm supporting disabled
OL,17,Fpeople around the world to do whatever
OL,18,Fthey like to do so that we can make
OL,19,Four world a slightly better place for
OL,20,Fpeople with a disability but also for
OL,21,Ftheir families."
